soldering.title: Soldering Iron Tip 40W (Conical B-Series for YIHUA947)
soldering.description: The B-series tips or conical shape are so named because of their pointed cone-like shape. Since it has a rounded tip, soldering can be done from any angle, and this tip is used for general purposes.

soldering.title: Solder Remover pump (Solder Vacuum)
soldering.description: The Solder Vacuum (pump) is tool for solder rework. It allows you to pull the molten solder out of a connection. To use it you simply depress the plunger, heat up your solder, place the nozzle over the solder you want to remove and finally just push the button. The piston pops up and the solder disappears.
